Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.steps

Class DefaultResponseStep<T>

java.lang.Object
oracle.kubernetes.operator.work.Step
oracle.kubernetes.operator.helpers.ResponseStep<T>
oracle.kubernetes.operator.steps.DefaultResponseStep<T>
public class DefaultResponseStep<T>
extends ResponseStep<T>
A response step which treats a NOT_FOUND status as success with a null result. By default, does nothing on success. Subclasses must override #doSuccess to take action.
